{"tid":2097703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民靜默舉白紙 警闖apm拘八人","createTime":"2020-07-07T04:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T04:22:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c3c5947ec37b7a2cd65f23d6559b998cdbbf1d","tid":2097703,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/2UF3G2V4FEAEC6JRIQJY2TDHPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2F2UF3G2V4FEAEC6JRIQJY2TDHPA%2F&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=9414bf02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2F2UF3G2V4FEAEC6JRIQJY2TDHPA%2F&h=70d3a9aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/2UF3G2V4FEAEC6JRIQJY2TDHPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n市民靜默舉白紙 警闖apm拘八人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EAIFoHkvTPi9TKFUO2s9T1w3gU4=/794x772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KZBEOG6R3KACJJFUSUXOOBKWYA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEAIFoHkvTPi9TKFUO2s9T1w3gU4%3D%2F794x772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKZBEOG6R3KACJJFUSUXOOBKWYA.gif&h=643e00fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名市民在觀塘apm舉白紙抗議，警闖商場稱市民涉非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日中環ifc及觀塘apm商場先後有活動抗議國安法，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n部份店舖被迫暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女子袋藏美國旗被帶走<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：逼網絡商提供用戶身份<br />\n<br />\n參與活動的李先生表示，港版國安法已通過，有得發聲就發聲，「最後一啖氣都要出來表達意見」。他批評政府漠視民意強推惡法，是「極權打壓不可原諒」，認為只會觸發更大民怨，「香港人唔會退縮」。<br />\n<br />\n警員一度離開，至7時重返現場，並進入各樓層截查，又在中庭拉起封鎖線，行人無法暢通行。7時10分，約十名防暴警員包圍一名中年女子，她被搜出背包內有一面美國旗，連同該名女子，警方合共帶走至少七人。7時45分，警員離開後，有人聚集叫口號及高唱《榮光》。至8時半左右，警第三度進入商場，舉起紫旗警告市民涉嫌違反國安法，最後帶走最少一男一女。警方表示全晚三男五女被捕，涉嫌參與未經批准集結及阻礙警員執行職務。<br />\n<br />\n昨午中環ifc有人舉行「和你Lunch」，近20人舉起白紙抗議。警方又再闖入私人物業，拍攝及截查市民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xos4oSUwV8wjZGPKn4Sm8b9jHow=/595x308/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YRJVOZVXS5AWQ5U3ZHHN4IHRQY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fxos4oSUwV8wjZGPKn4Sm8b9jHow%3D%2F595x308%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYRJVOZVXS5AWQ5U3ZHHN4IHRQY.gif&h=e26f7175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方在apm帶走最少八名市民。"},{"pid":"eaccde84aae630e5d8575ebcc9ca1cb9e1477965","tid":2097703,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497eae495f8500b6dd2f0d47043c85d57414bc29","tid":2097703,"uid":356476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c69b8e9234f629a75cadf5e32157fda695b0e6","tid":2097703,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}